def reverse(head): 
    prev = None
    cur = head 

    while cur:
        next = cur.next
        cur.next = prev 
        prev = cur 
        cur = next
    head = prev
    
    return head

def maxProfit(prices):
    min_price = float('inf')
    max_profit = 0

    for price in prices:
        min_price = min(min_price, price) 
        profit = price - min_price
        max_profit = max(max_profit, profit)

    return max_profit
